,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:23:09.000Z","msg":"廢游係16號寫信比英國<br />\n<br />\n而巴治奧前兩日先開po<br />\n<br />\n仲話以經驗之談<br />\n<br />\n咁成件事有咩問題呢 <br />\n<br />\n如果時序相反<br />\n<br />\n你呢個post都有得討論下<br />\n<br />\n但就算係掉轉時序<br />\n<br />\n我都覺得冇咩野<br />\n<br />\n因為我覺得一國兩制的確被破壞<br />\n<br />\n中英聯合聲明 英國其實都有義務幫下香港<br />\n<br />\n我舉個例子就係我地一路屌政府三權唔分立<br />\n<br />\n但又要佢接受我地對梁振英或其他高官既司法覆核<br />\n<br />\n難道你又會屌覆核王一路屌政府，一路要人接受你覆核<br />\n<br />\n各位有咩意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3934117d1c6520e01da9489e10da1c7d38667fb","tid":9981,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:24:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;死返去高登啦垃圾打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇吓我咩名先啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n熱狗過氣打手呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想搞到呢度變埋戰場？ 過主啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你一句熱狗過氣打手就想收人皮？<br />\n雖然樓主好有舊高登時事台風味，但唔係完全冇得討厭<br />\n唔好講到係熱狗支持者就唔洗理咁"},{"pid":"9b6d6fd49dec6667514d7c3bcc169e7dd785e044","tid":9981,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T01:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>&lt;blockquote&gt;&amp;lt;blockquote&amp;gt;死返去高登啦垃圾打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇吓我咩名先啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal